Subject: [PATCH] soundwire: intel_init: use eml_lock parameter
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e52cae0bb40c238c0ac1e6c2ff1fb63037fe741c
